================baksmali/smali================
https://github.com/JesusFreke/smali
https://bitbucket.org/JesusFreke/smali/downloads
================
usage: java -jar baksmali.jar [options] <dex-file>
disassembles and/or dumps a dex file
----------------
java -jar baksmali -o classout/ test.dex
================
usage: java -jar smali.jar [options] [--] [<smali-file>|folder]*
assembles a set of smali files into a dex file



================Apktool================
a tool for reengineering Android apk files
with smali and baksmali
----------------
https://ibotpeaches.github.io/Apktool
https://github.com/iBotPeaches/Apktool
https://bitbucket.org/iBotPeaches/apktool/downloads
================
Move both files (apktool.jar [link] & apktool [script]) 
to /usr/local/bin (root needed)
================
apktool d test.apk //Decoding
apktool b test //Building


================dex2jar================
https://github.com/pxb1988/dex2jar
================
dex2jar.bat classes.dex //2jar


================JD-GUI================
Java Decompiler
----------------
http://jd.benow.ca/
https://github.com/java-decompiler/jd-gui
================
java -jar jd-gui-1.4.0.jar 
